{"tid":942260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無辜公狗淪戀獸男性奴　下體失禁還每晚做噩夢","createTime":"2018-12-15T14:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T18:54:32.000Z","uid":212399,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2f6fb7f51d735d6b9beda7dcba24053a726c23de","tid":942260,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3760/d3760019.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3760%2Fd3760019.jpg&h=55b0791b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲品丘晚上時常作惡夢，即使入睡身體也會不斷發抖。（圖／翻攝自Facebook社團／RGSA Rescue Group for Spanish Animals）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n西班牙一隻公狗品丘（Pincho）從小遭到飼主的兄弟性侵，時間長達5年，下體嚴重撕裂傷，行走時會濺血，也造成失禁的後遺症。英國愛狗人士威絲特（Yvonne West）在Facebook上看到品丘的影片，背後的故事讓她於心不忍，今年5月領養了這隻身心受創的可憐狗狗。<br />\n據《太陽報》報導，今年5歲的品丘從出生開始，就被飼主的兄弟當作性奴，每周末都會性侵品丘洩慾，甚至蹂躪牠的下體，導致長期失禁以及濺血的問題，可憐的品丘步履艱難，行走間鮮血不時從腿間滑落。受到長期性侵的品丘，直到附近鄰居報警才被動保團體救出，然而依照西班牙法令，若要治罪獸姦者必須是現行犯，因此飼主兄弟倆至今仍未被逮捕與控罪。<br />\n在西班牙動保團體RGSA 的Facebook公開社團中，威絲特看到傷痕累累的品丘，決心跨海領養，現在品丘在英國的新家生活，得到良好的照顧和滿滿的愛，但她也表示，由於受到長期的性侵與虐待，下體失禁的問題難以根治，左腿也有骨折與推究等情況，更令人擔憂的是狗狗嚴重受創的內心。<br />\n威絲特說，品丘晚上時常作惡夢，即使入睡身體也會不斷發抖，經過長期的積極治療，品丘的情形逐漸好轉，「無論牠還能活多久，我都希望能讓牠在剩下的日子裡，過得美好又舒適。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://pets.ettoday.net/news/1329838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpets.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1329838&d=5jwT8us7VeZLNEszoRZoOb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=d23fa039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pets.ettoday.net/news/1329838</a>"},{"pid":"8c15e8cbbff31967dc5a6e474ece54f2eb6c8633","tid":942260,"uid":208817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733fcaafaf8d99a47c9a394f561c016206a399da","tid":942260,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2cb64f2b2d2d35090586fea65861b5f139255e","tid":942260,"uid":193893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:14:56.000Z","msg":"然而依照西班牙法令，若要治罪獸姦者必須是現行犯<br />\n<br />\n所謂捉賊就拿贓，捉姦就&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"d3fb6c364052f15de13ae8aa79075bcf1e06d747","tid":942260,"uid":86745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:19:11.000Z","msg":"鄰居點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d110a8ea7572637d3653c2a36858e4aa51c85189","tid":942260,"uid":24160,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:21:02.000Z","msg":"睇錯無辜狗公"},{"pid":"281bcf306beaea95a6cc54ed547d574b9466ce35","tid":942260,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:23:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9aa2d089d39f2fbd38fe6c268ce16834946a489e","tid":942260,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"281bcf306beaea95a6cc54ed547d574b9466ce35","tid":942260,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:23:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:29:56.000Z","msg":"可能春夢"},{"pid":"9f1d0081be46ceada4f9f5f7562a975940f0c2ad","tid":942260,"uid":139224,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:36:59.000Z","msg":"呢啲真係應該死刑"},{"pid":"b4120d0a6e7f7ae02d2a8fce4b127c060e176cc2","tid":942260,"uid":193893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9aa2d089d39f2fbd38fe6c268ce16834946a489e","tid":942260,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"281bcf306beaea95a6cc54ed547d574b9466ce35","tid":942260,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:23:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:29:56.000Z","msg":"可能春夢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:38:26.000Z","msg":"狗發夢會郁身郁勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog